<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Email Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .email-header {
      background: #2d89ef;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2d89ef;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .email-footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      background: #f9f9f9;
    }
    a {
      color: #2d89ef;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h2>Verify Your Email</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Please use the following verification code to activate your account. This code will expire in <strong>5 minutes</strong>.</p>
      
      <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>

      <p>If you did not register for an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Thank you,<br/>The Trinet Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at 
        <a href="mailto:rahimbadsa723.com">support@example.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
